<DOCNO>WT13-B20-53</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA079-000545-B017-271</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.cprn.com:80/health/johnmill.htm 207.102.137.115 19970211045145 text/html 5673
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Tue, 11 Feb 1997 04:51:56 GMT
