<html>
<head>
<title>Chart 1:  Annual Change in Employment</title>
<body  background=../pics/back4.gif text="#661621">
<P>
<table>
<tr>
<td align=left valign="top"><a href="../family/index.htm">
<img src="../pics/family2.gif"  alt="[Family]" vspace=5 hspace=20 width=70 border=0> </a><br>
<a href="../health/index.htm"><img src="../pics/health2.gif" alt="[Health]"   hspace=20 width=70 border=0> </a><br> 
<a href="../work/index.htm">
<img src="../pics/work2.gif" alt="[Work]" hspace=20 width=70 border=0></a><br>
<a href="../mailcprn.htm">
