<HTML><HEAD>  <META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Adobe PageMill 2.0 Mac">  <TITLE>New Year's Resolutions by Anne Hoover</TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff"><P><!- Page designed and coded by Gene Cowan> <!-MENU Bar Starts Here> <AHREF="../index.html"><IMG SRC="../images/main.gif" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="75"HEIGHT="43" HSPACE="0" VSPACE="0" BORDER="0" ALT="Main Menu" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0"></A> <TABLE BORDER="0" CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="0"><TR ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP"><TD><A HREF="../whats_new/new.html"><IMG SRC="../images/new.gif" ALIGN="LEFT"WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="20" HSPACE="0" VSPACE="0" BORDER="0" ALT="What's New"NATURALSIZEFLAG="0"></A></TD><TD><A HREF="../abcs_info/articles-info.html"><IMG SRC="../images/abc.gif" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="20" HSPACE="0" VSPACE="0" BORDER="0" ALT="ABCs" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0"></A></TD><TD><A HREF="../ld_indepth/resource-guide.html"><IMG SRC="../images/indepth.gif"ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="20" HSPACE="0" VSPACE="0" BORDER="0" ALT="In-Depth" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0"></A></TD><TD><A HREF="../finding_help/help.html"><IMG SRC="../images/help.gif" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="20" HSPACE="0" VSPACE="0" BORDER="0" ALT="Getting Help"NATURALSIZEFLAG="0"></A></TD><TD><A HREF="../ld_calendar/ld-calendar.html"><IMG SRC="../images/calendar.gif"ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="20" HSPACE="0" VSPACE="0" BORDER="0" ALT="Calendar" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0"></A></TD></TR><TR ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP"><TD><IMG SRC="../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="3" HSPACE="0"VSPACE="0" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0"></TD><TD><IMG SRC="../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="3" HSPACE="0"VSPACE="0" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0"></TD><TD><IMG SRC="../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="3" HSPACE="0"VSPACE="0" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0"></TD><TD><IMG SRC="../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="3" HSPACE="0"VSPACE="0" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0"></TD><TD><IMG SRC="../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="3" HSPACE="0"VSPACE="0" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0"></TD></TR><TR ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP"><TD><A HREF="../audio_clips/audio-clips.html"><IMG SRC="../images/audio.gif"ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="20" HSPACE="0" VSPACE="0" BORDER="0" ALT="Audio Clips" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0"></A></TD><TD><A HREF="http://www.capaccess.org/cgi-bin/ldonline/netforum/ldf/a/1"><IMG SRC="../images/bulletin.gif" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="20" HSPACE="0"VSPACE="0" BORDER="0" ALT="Bulletin Board" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0"></A></TD><TD><A HREF="../ld_store/LD-Store.html"><IMG SRC="../images/store.gif" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="20" HSPACE="0" VSPACE="0" BORDER="0" ALT="LD Store"NATURALSIZEFLAG="0"></A></TD><TD><A HREF="http://www.weta.capaccess.org/ldonline/ld_survey.html"><IMG SRC="../images/talk.gif" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="20" HSPACE="0" VSPACE="0"BORDER="0" ALT="Talk Back" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0"></A></TD><TD><A HREF="../kidzone/kidzone.html"><IMG SRC="../images/kid.gif" ALIGN="LEFT"WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="20" HSPACE="0" VSPACE="0" BORDER="0" ALT="Kid Zone" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0"></A></TD></TR></TABLE><BR><!-MENU Bar Ends Here> <BR><IMG SRC="../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="TOP" WIDTH="540" HEIGHT="3" VSPACE="0"NATURALSIZEFLAG="0"></P><H2 ALIGN=CENTER><TABLE WIDTH="304" HEIGHT="210" BORDER="0" CELLSPACING="2" CELLPADDING="0"><TR><TD WIDTH="30%" HEIGHT="126"><P ALIGN=RIGHT>&nbsp;<IMG SRC="../images/exclusive.gif" WIDTH="57" HEIGHT="66" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" ALIGN="TOP"></TD><TD WIDTH="70%"><P>&nbsp;</P><H2 ALIGN=CENTER>New Year's Resolutions<BR>for Parents and Teachers<BR>Working with LD Children</H2></TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2"><P ALIGN=CENTER>&nbsp;<B>By Anne Hoover <BR>The Kingsbury Center<BR>2138 Bancroft Place, N.W.<BR>Washington, D.C. 20008</B></TD></TR></TABLE></H2><P><IMG SRC="../images/bullets/Triangle/Triangle-red.gif" WIDTH="11" HEIGHT="11" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><B><FONT SIZE=+1>Resolution #1<BR></FONT></B>I will give &quot;think time&quot; before expecting a responseso that the child who has trouble finding the words he wants to use canbe prepared.</P><P><IMG SRC="../images/bullets/Triangle/Triangle-blue.gif" WIDTH="11" HEIGHT="11" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><B><FONT SIZE=+1>Resolution #2<BR></FONT></B>I will make eye contact or use touch when I want a child's attention.</P><P><IMG SRC="../images/bullets/Triangle/Triangle-red.gif" WIDTH="11" HEIGHT="11" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><B><FONT SIZE=+1>Resolution #3 <BR></FONT></B>If a child asks me to repeat what I said, I will do so usingdifferent and, perhaps, simpler language.</P><P><IMG SRC="../images/bullets/Triangle/Triangle-blue.gif" WIDTH="11" HEIGHT="11" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><B><FONT SIZE=+1>Resolution #4</FONT></B><BR>I will find a subject area in which my child is interested and help herbecome an expert in it.</P><P><IMG SRC="../images/bullets/Triangle/Triangle-red.gif" WIDTH="11" HEIGHT="11" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><B><FONT SIZE=+1>Resolution #5</FONT><BR></B>When my child's attention wanders, I will use a secret signal to alerthim to tune back in.</P><P><IMG SRC="../images/bullets/Triangle/Triangle-blue.gif" WIDTH="11" HEIGHT="11" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><B><FONT SIZE=+1>Resolution #6</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=+1> </FONT><BR>I will always point out the positive aspects of a child's work before focusingon the areas that need improvement.</P><P><IMG SRC="../images/bullets/Triangle/Triangle-red.gif" WIDTH="11" HEIGHT="11" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><B><FONT SIZE=+1>Resolution #7</FONT></B><BR>I will make transitions from one activity to another easier for a childby giving her periodic time updates so that she can complete the first activityand get ready for the next one.</P><P><IMG SRC="../images/bullets/Triangle/Triangle-blue.gif" WIDTH="11" HEIGHT="11" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><B><FONT SIZE=+1>Resolution #8</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=+1> </FONT><BR>I will model my thinking and organization strategies by thinking aloud somy child can develop his own inner language.</P><P><IMG SRC="../images/bullets/Triangle/Triangle-red.gif" WIDTH="11" HEIGHT="11" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><B><FONT SIZE=+1>Resolution #9</FONT><BR></B>I will teach my child to make a &quot;mental movie&quot; and then tellabout it to help her connect language to visual images.</P><P><IMG SRC="../images/bullets/Triangle/Triangle-blue.gif" WIDTH="11" HEIGHT="11" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><B><FONT SIZE=+1>Resolution #10</FONT></B><BR>I will remember that all children want to please and be successful. If achild gives the impression of not caring about his work or behavior, itis to protect himself from failure. Developing short term goals that thechild can reach will lead to success.</P><P>&nbsp;</P><P ALIGN=CENTER>The Kingsbury Center is a nonprofit educational organizationthat provides comprehensive <BR>services to support children and adults with learning disabilities throughits <BR>Tutoring Services, Assessment Services and Kingsbury Day School. <BR>E-mail: <A HREF="mailto:kngsbryctr@aol.com">KNGSBRYCTR@AOL.COM</A></P><P ALIGN=CENTER><BR><BR><HR SIZE="3" NOSHADE><BR></P><P ALIGN=CENTER><FONT SIZE=-2>&copy;1996 WETA</FONT></BODY></HTML>
