a_earlyid.html">Early Identification of Speech &amp; Language  Delays and Disorders</A>, American Speech-Language-Hearing Association's</B>  helpful booklet on early warning signs.</MENU><H3>Learn more about it:</H3><MENU>  <P><A HREF="../../finding_help/publications_help/speech_language_pubs.html"><B>Our  selection of publications</B></A> will provide sources for more in-depth  learning.</MENU><P><HR ALIGN=LEFT SIZE="3" WIDTH="540%" NOSHADE><BR></P><P ALIGN=CENTER><FONT SIZE=-2>&copy;1996 WETA</FONT></BODY></HTML>
