ition services. <BR>  <BR>  <B><A HREF="../iep/ieppub.html">Transition Services in the I.E.P.</A>,  NICHCY Digest, 1993 -</B> A comprehensive guide to understanding transition  services, including extensive resource listings.</MENU><P><HR ALIGN=LEFT SIZE="3" WIDTH="540%" NOSHADE><BR></P><P ALIGN=CENTER><FONT SIZE=-2>&copy;1996 WETA</FONT></BODY></HTML>
