<P>
The <A HREF="#anchor736382">National Organizations</A> respond to questions
personally. The <A HREF="#anchor738030">Other National Toll-Free Numbers</A>
are for other national organizations that are concerned with disability
and children's issues. Inclusion on this list does not imply endorsement
by its source (NICHCY, the National Center for Information on Children and
Youth with Disabilities, or LD OnLine. Telephone numbers are designated
as either Voice (V) or Text Telephone (TTY), indicating their accessibility
to TTY users. <BR>
<BR>
