<B>Other Resources:</B><BR>
<BR>
For individuals with a computer and modem, there are on-line bulletin boards
where parents, adults<BR>
with ADHD, and medical professionals share experiences, offer emotional
support, and ask and<BR>
respond to questions. <BR>
<BR>
Two such on-line services include CompuServe [(800) 848-8990] and America
Online [(800)<BR>
827-6364]. You may also wish to check with other national and local on-line
communications<BR>
companies to see if they offer similar services. <BR>
