shers, 1992. ISBN 1561450251<BR><BR><B>Social Competence of Young Children with Disabilities: Issues and Strategiesfor Intervention.</B> Samuel Odom, Scott McConnell, and Mary McEvoy, PaulBrookes Publishing Co., 1992. ISBN 1557660859<BR><BR><B>No One to Play with: The Social Side of Learning Disabilities,</B> BettyOsman, Academic Therapy Publications, 1982. ISBN 0879796878<BR></P><P ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="pub_dist_list.html">Publishers &amp; DistributorsListing</A></P><P><HR ALIGN=LEFT SIZE="3" WIDTH="540%" NOSHADE></P><P ALIGN=CENTER><FONT SIZE=-2>&copy;1996 WETA</FONT></BODY></HTML>
